    "body": "This is why I want the TickTank PR merged, you can then use a set of upgrades to upgrade the Attack\\* trait instead of the Armaments trait.\n\nOn the other hand, there is a workaround already to your problem, use proper planning and layers. If there's three upgrades possible for that unit, then set that one upgrade grants it one level, the next two and the next one four. then set it up like a table\n\n0 1 - first upgrade enabled\n2 3 - second upgrade mixed with first\n4 5 - third upgrade enabled mixed with first\n6 7 - all three upgrades can be enabled.\n"
